最近、こんなコンポーネント作った
```&lt;Authorized allowRole="ROLE_KEY_A"&gt;Authorized&lt;/Authorized&gt;
&lt;Authorized every allowRole={['ROLE_KEY_A', 'ROLE_KEY_B']}&gt;Authorized&lt;/Authorized&gt;
&lt;Authorized some allowRole={['ROLE_KEY_A', 'ROLE_KEY_B']}&gt;Authorized&lt;/Authorized&gt;
&lt;Authorized allowRole="ROLE_KEY_A" fallback={&lt;p&gt;Unauthorized&lt;/p&gt;}&gt;Authorized&lt;/Authorized&gt;```
